## Shrunk to 100px so she reads as a small, lithe water spirit relative to
## the burlier Vikings. Her 48×48 source frames fill the whole canvas (no
## transparent padding), so a given pixel height makes her look visually
## larger than other creatures whose art leaves breathing room — hence
## the lower target.
target_display_height = 100.0

